If you’re experiencing fear while listening to a politician, “It is important to understand that many statements made by politicians and candidates are made for strategic reasons that extend beyond changing your vote to demobilizing the electorate,” says Huddy (Political Psychology, Vol. 32, No. 3, 2011).

DARK TRIAD TRAIT
in 2010, Dr Peter Jonason, then assistant professor of psychology at the University of Western Florida, and his co-author, Gregory Webster, assistant professor of psychology at the University of Florida, developed the "Dirty Dozen" rating scale, or a 12-item methodology, to measure Dark Triad traits. [1]

Jonason and Webster's measure asks people to rate themselves against these questions:

I tend to manipulate others to get my way.
I have used deceit or lied to get my way.
I have used flattery to get my way.
I tend to exploit others towards my own end.
I tend to lack remorse.
I tend to not be too concerned with morality or the morality of my actions.
I tend to be callous or insensitive.
I tend to be cynical.
I tend to want others to admire me.
I tend to want others to pay attention to me.
I tend to seek prestige or status.
I tend to expect special favors from others.

Nice video. But India in a Digital Chakravyuh now. India's heavy reliance on foreign operating systems like Microsoft, Google and social media platforms like Facebook, Instagram, and WhatsApp highlights a critical vulnerability in our digital infrastructure. Indians have enthusiastically embraced foreign social media and tech platforms, using them as their own, entering this digital Chakravyuha with ease.

You cannot build your digital ecosystem in someone else's backyard. India needs our own Google, Microsoft and Social media apps. It might take some and lot of resources but that doesn't mean we should not do it! 

A nation this large cannot play second fiddle to some power that lies across the Atlantic. India needs to develop its own operating systems and social media platforms or risk dancing to the tunes of what foreign powers want it to play, becoming a poster child of digital neo-colonialism.

How long? This is a question Indians themselves need to answer. As populism increasingly dictates policy, Indians have a major role to play in this matter, perhaps even more than the Indian government.

While I agree with the tracking part, I don't think ChatGPT is a good replacement of Google, and here's why.
ChatGPT's knowledge is based on training data (Basically it doesn't have the info of the present data), whereas google aggregates the data actively with the web crawlers running continuously to rank and index the resources. From LLM perspective, yeah definitely go for ChatGPT.
Also, there are some Search Engines which doesn't track, e.g. DuckDuckGo, but I still use Google, because of it's reliability. (Bing is also good, but not at the level of Google).

Dhruv Rathee ek pramukh Indian YouTuber aur samajik commentator hain, jinhonne digital charcha ke kshetra mein apna ek mahatvapurna sthan banaya hai. Unki yatra engineering ke vidyarthi hone se lekar samajik aur rajneetik tark par dhyan kendrit karne mein ek gehra sankalp dikhati hai, jo sachai ki khoj aur samaj sudhar ke prati purn hai.

Dhruv Rathee ke prabhav ka mool karan unki tathya par aadharit pratibaddhta aur pransparansyata mein hai. Aaj kal, jahan galat jaankari bina rok tok phail rahi hai, Rathee ki mahatvapurna anusandhan aur satikata se bhari pravritti ek nayi disha pradan karti hai. Sarkari nitiyon ko vyakul karne, bhram ko khndit karne ya samajik arthik mudde par vichar karne mein, unka content data aur vishwasniya srot se sajiv hota hai. Yeh gyan ke dware unke darshakon ko prabhavit karne ke saath-saath unhe samajhne aur vyavharik roop se samajhne ki shamta bhi pradan karta hai.

Rathee ke online upasthiti ka mool madhya hai unki sarkari prashasan mein pransparansyata aur uttaradayitv ki avdharna. Unki jasoosi patrakarita aur khulase se, ve bhrashtachar, vyapari prabhav aur niti viphalataon par prakash dalte hain jo samanya nagrikon par prabhav dalte hain. Unki sahasi sach ki khoj ne kayi bar prashasanik shaktiyo par sawal uthaya hai, jisse ve samajik nyay aur sarkari uttaradayitv ke lie pramukh awaz ban gaye hain.

Iske alawa, Rathee ka samarthan rashtriya simaon se pare, jaise jalvayu parivartan, antarrashtriya rajniti aur manav adhikaron jaise global mudde ko bhi samete hai. Unke darshakon ke beech vishvavirodhi drishti ko badhane ke madhyam se, ve ekjut aur samanvay se duniya bhar ke samasyaon ka samna karne mein sahayak hain.

Unke content ki buddhiman gahrai ke alawa, Rathee ka naitik drishtikon aur imandari unke darshakon ke mann mein gehra prabhav chhodta hai. Ve vyapari prabhav ya rajneetik samarthan se swatantr roop se kam karte hain, jisse unka tark patrakarita aur mukt ho jaata hai. Is prakar ke patrakarita ki samartha ne unhe ek vishwasniya gyan aur vichar ki pramukh srot banaya hai ek digital awaz ke yug mein.

Aur bhi, Rathee ka prabhav digital vishwa se bahar jaata hai, jo asli jeevan mein parinat hota hai. Unka samarthan samajik andolanon ko prabhavit karta hai, janta ke madhyam se charcha ko prakashit karta hai aur nitiyaan ki vichar dhara ko prabhavit karta hai. Grassroots karyakarta aur samudayik gatividhiyon ke madhyam se, ve apne darshakon ko sakriy bhaagidar banane ke liye prerit karte hain, jo ek adhik nyayapoorn aur samaveshi samaj ki ore agrasar kar raha hai.

Ant mein, Dhruv Rathee digital media ke prabhav ko darshata hai jo janta ko gyan se paripurn nagrikta mein badalne aur samajik nyay ke liye prabhavit karne mein sahayak hai. Unki sachai, pransparansyata aur naitik patrakarita ke mool mein, unhe vishva bhar ke ek vichar-dhara ki jyoti samaj mein sthapit hoti hai. Jaise hi ve apne prabhav ko badhate hain aur vyapak karte hain, Rathee ek nayi pidi ko pragatishil nagrik hone ka sahas pradan karte hain jo loktantrik mulyon aur samajik pragati ke liye samarjit hai.

Ever since Mr Shinde has become the Chief Minister many things have happened to improve on the infrastructure.

1) There is a six lane proposed road between Thane and Borivali, but for the common man we need a metro line along this route it will cut down travel time
2) One more metro needed between Mulund and Goregaon

5) We can build commercial complex above our Bus depots to earn more revenue. In Hong Kong and Singapore they have a bus depot on the Ground floor. Metro line on the first, Parking from 2nd to 5th Shopping Complex  from 5th  to 10th. Commercial offices, Restraunts and Hotels from 7th to 60th floor. 8) Lots of factories have closed down in and around Mumbai.  This is natural progress. We need to create more centers of employment. This is happening . प्राइवेट स्कूल वाले बाहर निकाल दे तो कहा जायेंगे? दुनिया का पहला ऐसा डिप्लोमा है एक ही जगह पढ़ा सकते रह सकते एक ही डिप्लोमा दो जगह अलग अलग मान्य हो गया गोवर्मेंट के लिये अलग, प्राइवेट के लिए अलग मान्य है? ईसी दिन के लिए NIOS DELED करवाया था MHRD, NCTE और NIOS ने ? सबसे बड़ा दोषी MHRD है, हमसे दो साल बोल के पैसा ठगने का काम किया, मोदी जी का फोटो लगा हुआ विज्ञापन देख कर लाखो कैंडिडेट ने रजिस्ट्रेशन करना शुरू किया, उस समय के NIOS चेयरमैन ने भरोषा दिलाया की हर जगह मान्य है, नहीं तो इसमे कुता बिल्ली भी ऐडमिशन नहीं करवाते, पहले ही बोल देते आप कही भी आगे गोवर्मेंट सर्विस के लिए पात्र नहीं होंगे, तो हम प्राइवेट स्कूल वाले क्यों करते ये मोदी जी का बकवास कोर्स जब भविष्य मे NIOS DELED का कही प्रयोग ही नहीं होता! एक ही जगह आठ से दस हजार रुपये के लिये बंधुआ मंजदुर के लिए क्यों भला कोई ये करता, pvt स्कूल के शिक्षक को भी लपेटा गया सिर्फ पैसे के लिये उनका भी जिंदगी खराब कर दिया, MHRD के आदेश पर 2 साल का पढाई (सिलेबस) हमसे 18 महीने मे करवाया और 6 महीने का प्रशिक्षण जो स्कूल मे पढ़या जाता है उनको करने की जरूरत नहीं है क्यों की ये पहले से कही ना कहीं पढ़ा रहे है इसलिये इनको करने की जरूरत नहीं है इनके पास बाकी रेगुलर डिप्लोमा वाले से जयदा अनुभव है ये कहना था उस समय के मंत्री अधिकारियों का, ये व्यान उस समय के MHRD मिनिस्टर प्रकाश जावेडकर जी का ऑन रेकॉड् व्यान है, कोर्स का प्रारूप तो गोवर्मेंट और उनकी संस्था ने मिल कर तैयार किया, तो इसमे हमारी क्या गलती है, हमने तो नहीं कहा की आप 18 महीने मे कराओ? इसमे गलती किसकी है? आज 14 लाख कैंडिडेट का भविष्य बर्बाद कर दिया, हमारा पैसा समय कौन लौटायेगा? इन सबने हमारा भविष्य बर्बाद कर दिया, देश 14 लाख अभ्यर्थी को मुर्ख बनाया, 420 का केस बनता इन सब पर! हम सुप्रिम कोर्ट से हार चुके है, अब हमें शिक्षा मंत्रालय और उनकी संस्था NCTE, NIOS से लड़ना है, पूर्व के मंत्री और जो अध्यक्ष थे उनसे लड़ना है वो साक्षी है इस NIOS DELED के जिंहोने करवाया इनकी लापरवाही से हमारा जिन्दगी खराब हुई, इन सब पर धोख़ा दड़ी केस होना चाहिए तभी जा के कुछ हो सकता है, ऐसे मान्यता के लिये लड़े तो हार जायेंगे केस खारिज हो सकता है पहले ही इसका निर्णय हो चुका है! अब चुप बैठने से नहीं होगा सबको साथ आना होगा जमीन पर मिल कर काम करना होगा सत्ता पक्ष और विपक्ष के नेताओ से मिलना होगा उनको बताना होगा हमारे से गलत हुआ है! हम सब राष्ट्रपति से इक्षा मृत्यु देने की माँग करेंगे, या इक्षा मृत्यु दे नहीं तो डिप्लोमा को मान्य करे!

सर 1.5 लाख युवा का भविष्य आपके हाथ में हे 
14/june/2022 ko हमारी डिफेंस की *जॉइनिंग कैंसिल हो गई  गवर्नमेंट की Agniveer* योजना के कारण हमने आपको Mail भी करें पर आपने हमारी Mail देखी नही हे 
 hamari army /airforce ki recruitment 2019-22 k beech mein dekhi thii jiske liye humne bahut mehnat ki thi...hume baar baar dhoka diya gya sarkar k dwara ki jld hi aapki recruitment ko complete krdiya jayega Recruitment office's par vist krne par hume yeh kaha gya ki chinta mat kijiye aapko aapki joining mil jayegi sirf kuch administrative reason chl rahe hai...Aisa bol kr hume 1-1.5 saal tak dhoke mein rkha gya..fir ek din 14 June 2022 ko agnipath scheme ko launch Kiya gya or humse kaha gya ki aapki jo bhi recruitment kisi bhi stage par thi usko hum cancel krte hai..Hume iss recruitment k liye hrr sambhav prayas kiya hum Defence minister Rajnath Singh ji se bhi mile unhone Hume yeh aaswasan diya ki chinta mat kijiye aapki recruitment process ko hum complete krenge or aapko joining denge but woh apni baat se plat gye...sir humne bahut mehnat ki thii fooj ki wardi ko paane k liye...hum sab gareeb ghr k bcche hai...hamari recruitment ko cancel krne par desh mein 64+ bccho ne suicide krliya tha...hum aapse yeh aagrah krte hai ki aap hamare liye aawaj ko uthaiye..scheme launch hone se pehle hi recruitment ko complete krliya tha...sir kya fooj ka sapna dekhna yeh hamari sabse badi galti thii...hum roj ghut ghut k marte hai..khud ko face tak nhi krpate hai...jhaa humne khud ko ek fooj ka part bnte dekha thaa whaa par hum aaj majdoori krr rahe hai

 hamari army /airforce ki recruitment 2019-22 k beech mein dekhi thii jiske liye humne bahut mehnat ki thi...hume baar baar dhoka diya gya sarkar k dwara ki jld hi aapki recruitment ko complete krdiya jayega Recruitment office's par vist krne par hume yeh kaha gya ki chinta mat kijiye aapko aapki joining mil jayegi sirf kuch administrative reason chl rahe hai...Aisa bol kr hume 1-1.5 saal tak dhoke mein rkha gya..fir ek din 14 June 2022 ko agnipath scheme ko launch Kiya gya or humse kaha gya ki aapki jo bhi recruitment kisi bhi stage par thi usko hum cancel krte hai..Hume iss recruitment k liye hrr sambhav prayas kiya hum Defence minister Rajnath Singh ji se bhi mile unhone Hume yeh aaswasan diya ki chinta mat kijiye aapki recruitment process ko hum complete krenge or aapko joining denge but woh apni baat se plat gye...sir humne bahut mehnat ki thii fooj ki wardi ko paane k liye...hum sab gareeb ghr k bcche hai...hamari recruitment ko cancel krne par desh mein 64+ bccho ne suicide krliya tha...hum aapse yeh aagrah krte hai ki aap hamare liye aawaj ko uthaiye..scheme launch hone se pehle hi recruitment ko complete krliya tha...sir kya fooj ka sapna dekhna yeh hamari sabse badi galti thii...hum roj ghut ghut k marte hai..khud ko face tak nhi krpate hai...jhaa humne khud ko ek fooj ka part bnte dekha thaa whaa par hum aaj majdoori krr rahe hai
 *Apki 1 vedio hmare घर में उजाला kr skti he प्लीज सर हमारे लिए वीडियो बना दो*

 hamari army /airforce ki recruitment 2019-22 k beech mein dekhi thii jiske liye humne bahut mehnat ki thi...hume baar baar dhoka diya gya sarkar k dwara ki jld hi aapki recruitment ko complete krdiya jayega Recruitment office's par vist krne par hume yeh kaha gya ki chinta mat kijiye aapko aapki joining mil jayegi sirf kuch administrative reason chl rahe hai...Aisa bol kr hume 1-1.5 saal tak dhoke mein rkha gya..fir ek din 14 June 2022 ko agnipath scheme ko launch Kiya gya or humse kaha gya ki aapki jo bhi recruitment kisi bhi stage par thi usko hum cancel krte hai..Hume iss recruitment k liye hrr sambhav prayas kiya hum Defence minister Rajnath Singh ji se bhi mile unhone Hume yeh aaswasan diya ki chinta mat kijiye aapki recruitment process ko hum complete krenge or aapko joining denge but woh apni baat se plat gye...sir humne bahut mehnat ki thii fooj ki wardi ko paane k liye...hum sab gareeb ghr k bcche hai...hamari recruitment ko cancel krne par desh mein 64+ bccho ne suicide krliya tha...hum aapse yeh aagrah krte hai ki aap hamare liye aawaj ko uthaiye..scheme launch hone se pehle hi recruitment ko complete krliya tha...sir kya fooj ka sapna dekhna yeh hamari sabse badi galti thii...hum roj ghut ghut k marte hai..khud ko face tak nhi krpate hai...jhaa humne khud ko ek fooj ka part bnte dekha thaa whaa par hum aaj majdoori krr rahe hai
 *Apki 1 vedio hmare घर में उजाला kr skti he प्लीज सर हमारे लिए वीडियो बना दो*

 hamari army /airforce ki recruitment 2019-22 k beech mein dekhi thii jiske liye humne bahut mehnat ki thi...hume baar baar dhoka diya gya sarkar k dwara ki jld hi aapki recruitment ko complete krdiya jayega Recruitment office's par vist krne par hume yeh kaha gya ki chinta mat kijiye aapko aapki joining mil jayegi sirf kuch administrative reason chl rahe hai...Aisa bol kr hume 1-1.5 saal tak dhoke mein rkha gya..fir ek din 14 June 2022 ko agnipath scheme ko launch Kiya gya or humse kaha gya ki aapki jo bhi recruitment kisi bhi stage par thi usko hum cancel krte hai..Hume iss recruitment k liye hrr sambhav prayas kiya hum Defence minister Rajnath Singh ji se bhi mile unhone Hume yeh aaswasan diya ki chinta mat kijiye aapki recruitment process ko hum complete krenge or aapko joining denge but woh apni baat se plat gye...sir humne bahut mehnat ki thii fooj ki wardi ko paane k liye...hum sab gareeb ghr k bcche hai...hamari recruitment ko cancel krne par desh mein 64+ bccho ne suicide krliya tha...hum aapse yeh aagrah krte hai ki aap hamare liye aawaj ko uthaiye..scheme launch hone se pehle hi recruitment ko complete krliya tha...sir kya fooj ka sapna dekhna yeh hamari sabse badi galti thii...hum roj ghut ghut k marte hai..khud ko face tak nhi krpate hai...jhaa humne khud ko ek fooj ka part bnte dekha thaa whaa par hum aaj majdoori krr rahe hai
 *Apki 1 vedio hmare घर में उजाला kr skti he प्लीज सर हमारे लिए वीडियो बना दो*

सर 1.5 लाख युवा का भविष्य आपके हाथ में हे 
14/june/2022 ko हमारी डिफेंस की *जॉइनिंग कैंसिल हो गई  गवर्नमेंट की Agniveer* योजना के कारण हमने आपको Mail भी करें पर आपने हमारी Mail देखी नही हे 
 hamari army /airforce ki recruitment 2019-22 k beech mein dekhi thii jiske liye humne bahut mehnat ki thi...hume baar baar dhoka diya gya sarkar k dwara ki jld hi aapki recruitment ko complete krdiya jayega Recruitment office's par vist krne par hume yeh kaha gya ki chinta mat kijiye aapko aapki joining mil jayegi sirf kuch administrative reason chl rahe hai...Aisa bol kr hume 1-1.5 saal tak dhoke mein rkha gya..fir ek din 14 June 2022 ko agnipath scheme ko launch Kiya gya or humse kaha gya ki aapki jo bhi recruitment kisi bhi stage par thi usko hum cancel krte hai..Hume iss recruitment k liye hrr sambhav prayas kiya hum Defence minister Rajnath Singh ji se bhi mile unhone Hume yeh aaswasan diya ki chinta mat kijiye aapki recruitment process ko hum complete krenge or aapko joining denge but woh apni baat se plat gye...sir humne bahut mehnat ki thii fooj ki wardi ko paane k liye...hum sab gareeb ghr k bcche hai...hamari recruitment ko cancel krne par desh mein 64+ bccho ne suicide krliya tha...hum aapse yeh aagrah krte hai ki aap hamare liye aawaj ko uthaiye..scheme launch hone se pehle hi recruitment ko complete krliya tha...sir kya fooj ka sapna dekhna yeh hamari sabse badi galti thii...hum roj ghut ghut k marte hai..khud ko face tak nhi krpate hai...jhaa humne khud ko ek fooj ka part bnte dekha thaa whaa par hum aaj majdoori krr rahe hai
 *Apki 1 vedio hmare घर में उजाला kr skti he प्लीज सर हमारे लिए वीडियो बना दो* 
Please sir hamari aawaj ko raise krne mein hamari help kijiye

मैं गुजरात राज्य में सरकारी शिक्षक की नौकरी के लिए एक योग्य उम्मीदवार हूं और हम नौकरी के लिए सरकार के खिलाफ विरोध प्रदर्शन कर रहे हैं। गुजरात सरकार ने ज्ञान सहायक की शुरुआत की है जो योग्य उम्मीदवारों को स्थायी नौकरियां देने के बजाय अनुबंध आधारित नौकरी है। हमने आज गांधीनगर में विरोध प्रदर्शन किया लेकिन पुलिस बेरहमी से 800 से अधिक अभ्यर्थियों को हिरासत में ले रही है और उन्हें जाने नहीं दे रही है। वे हमारे साथ आतंकवादियों जैसा व्यवहार कर रहे हैं। राज्य सरकार का कोई भी व्यक्ति इस मुद्दे के समाधान के लिए आगे नहीं आया है और यह लड़ाई 1 साल से चल रही है। कृपया समस्या का समाधान करें क्योंकि हमें आप जैसे लोगों के समर्थन की आवश्यकता है। 

कृपया मदद करें यह गुजरात में शिक्षा के भविष्य के बारे में है। यहां की जनता अंधी और बहरी है, वह धर्म के नाम पर वोट दे रही है, लेकिन उसे यहां के स्कूलों की खराब हालत दिखाई नहीं दे रही है। सरकारी शिक्षकों की 74 हजार से ज्यादा सीटें खाली हैं फिर भी नौकरी नहीं दे रहे हैं. हमारी मदद करें हमें आपके समर्थन की आवश्यकता है।

सर 1.5 लाख युवा का भविष्य आपके हाथ में हे 
14/june/2022 ko हमारी डिफेंस की *जॉइनिंग कैंसिल हो गई  गवर्नमेंट की Agniveer* योजना के कारण हमने आपको Mail भी करें पर आपने हमारी Mail देखी नही हे 
 hamari army /airforce ki recruitment 2019-22 k beech mein dekhi thii jiske liye humne bahut mehnat ki thi...hume baar baar dhoka diya gya sarkar k dwara ki jld hi aapki recruitment ko complete krdiya jayega Recruitment office's par vist krne par hume yeh kaha gya ki chinta mat kijiye aapko aapki joining mil jayegi sirf kuch administrative reason chl rahe hai...Aisa bol kr hume 1-1.5 saal tak dhoke mein rkha gya..fir ek din 14 June 2022 ko agnipath scheme ko launch Kiya gya or humse kaha gya ki aapki jo bhi recruitment kisi bhi stage par thi usko hum cancel krte hai..Hume iss recruitment k liye hrr sambhav prayas kiya hum Defence minister Rajnath Singh ji se bhi mile unhone Hume yeh aaswasan diya ki chinta mat kijiye aapki recruitment process ko hum complete krenge or aapko joining denge but woh apni baat se plat gye...sir humne bahut mehnat ki thii fooj ki wardi ko paane k liye...hum sab gareeb ghr k bcche hai...hamari recruitment ko cancel krne par desh mein 64+ bccho ne suicide krliya tha...hum aapse yeh aagrah krte hai ki aap hamare liye aawaj ko uthaiye..scheme launch hone se pehle hi recruitment ko complete krliya tha...sir kya fooj ka sapna dekhna yeh hamari sabse badi galti thii...hum roj ghut ghut k marte hai..khud ko face tak nhi krpate hai...jhaa humne khud ko ek fooj ka part bnte dekha thaa whaa par hum aaj majdoori krr rahe hai
 *Apki 1 vedio hmare घर में उजाला kr skti he प्लीज सर हमारे लिए वीडियो बना दो* 
Please sir hamari aawaj ko raise krne mein hamari help kijiye

Dear Dhruv,

We hope this message finds you well. We are N.I.O.S D.EL.Ed candidates, and we are writing on behalf of the N.I.O.S D.El.Ed teachers from across the country. We are facing a critical issue that has affected approximately 14 lakh untrained teachers who were employed in government and private primary schools across India. Your platform has the power to bring our plight to the forefront, and we earnestly request your support in ventilating our voice throughout India.

Background Information:

With due respect, we would like to inform you that we are N.I.O.S D.El.Ed Teachers from across the country. According to the RTE-2009, every child has the fundamental right to receive primary education from a trained teacher. To ensure the fundamental rights of children, the Indian government passed a bill in both houses of Parliament with consensus in 2017. Through this, government, government-aided, and private school teachers who were untrained as of the 2010 NCTE notification were given the opportunity to complete the D.El.Ed course through NIOS. Thereafter, the Ministry of Human Resource Development (MHRD) issued a letter to all the Secretaries of States and Union Territories, directing that all teachers in government schools must possess minimum qualifications as mandated under the Right to Education Act, 2009, and a last chance was given to all teachers to acquire the same by March 31, 2019.

In 2017, the Modi government urged us to enroll in the Diploma in Elementary Education (D.El.Ed) conducted by N.I.O.S. Approximately 14 lakh untrained teachers, who were already employed in government and private primary schools across the country, enrolled. Subsequently, NCTE issued a recognition order to be published in the Gazette, thereby conducting the D.El.Ed program through the Open and Distance Learning (ODL) mode by NIOS, which reduced the duration of the program from 2 years to 18 months. Education Minister Prakash Javadekar (at that time) and our PM Narendra Damodardas Modi emphasized our enrollment in the Diploma in Elementary Education (D.El.Ed) through the National Institute of Open Schooling (NIOS). Normally, the program of the course is 2 years (18 months of theory and 6 months of internship), but our course was completed within 2 sessions (18 months) as we were already employed and did not require an internship. NIOS Board conducted all the exams for this course. It was promoted by Prime Minister Narendra Modi.

Current Situation:

According to the rules, this new plan of NCTE and the Modi government had to be published in the Gazette, but NCTE did not comply. As a result, in 2023, after 7 years, the Honourable Supreme Court announced that our degree is not valid for new recruitment. We cannot apply for any new recruitment in government schools and will not be able to do so in the future due to the negligence of NCTE and the false guarantee by Modi. Due to this mistake by Narendra Modi, today, 14 lakh families are suffering, with no solution in sight.

Our Request:

We, the 14 lakh affected teachers, humbly request your support to highlight our situation on your channel. Your influence and reach can help us gain the attention of the authorities and the public, potentially leading to a resolution of our predicament. We believe that with your help, we can bring our issue to the forefront and seek justice for the countless teachers who have dedicated their lives to educating the children of our country.

Thank you for your time and consideration. We sincerely hope that you will be able to support us in this crucial matter.

Warm regards,

N.I.O.S D.EL.Ed SONGAMI MONCHO

 hamari army /airforce ki recruitment 2019-22 k beech mein dekhi thii jiske liye humne bahut mehnat ki thi...hume baar baar dhoka diya gya sarkar k dwara ki jld hi aapki recruitment ko complete krdiya jayega Recruitment office's par visit krne par hume yeh kaha gya ki chinta mat kijiye aapko aapki joining mil jayegi sirf kuch administrative reason chl rahe hai...Aisa bol kr hume 1-1.5 saal tak dhoke mein rkha gya..fir ek din 14 June 2022 ko agnipath scheme ko launch Kiya gya or humse kaha gya ki aapki jo bhi recruitment kisi bhi stage par thi usko hum cancel krte hai..Hume iss recruitment k liye hrr sambhav prayas kiya hum Defence minister Rajnath Singh ji se bhi mile unhone Hume yeh aaswasan diya ki chinta mat kijiye aapki recruitment process ko hum complete krenge or aapko joining denge but woh apni baat se palat gye...sir humne bahut mehnat ki thii fooj ki wardi ko paane k liye...hum sab gareeb ghr k bcche hai...hamari recruitment ko cancel krne par desh mein 64+ bccho ne suicide bhi  kiya  tha but kisi ko in bato se koi fark ni pdta...hum aapse yeh aagrah krte hai ki aap hamare liye aawaj ko uthaiye..scheme launch hone se pehle hi recruitment ko complete krliya tha...sir kya fooj ka sapna dekhna yeh hamari sabse badi galti thii...hum roj ghut ghut k marte hai..khud ko face tak nhi krpate hai...jhaa humne khud ko ek fooj ka part bnte dekha thaa whaa par hum aaj majdoori krr rahe hai
 *Apki 1 video hmare घर में उजाला kr skti he प्लीज सर हमारे लिए वीडियो बना दो*

 hamari army /airforce ki recruitment 2019-22 k beech mein dekhi thii jiske liye humne bahut mehnat ki thi...hume baar baar dhoka diya gya sarkar k dwara ki jld hi aapki recruitment ko complete krdiya jayega Recruitment office's par vist krne par hume yeh kaha gya ki chinta mat kijiye aapko aapki joining mil jayegi sirf kuch administrative reason chl rahe hai...Aisa bol kr hume 1-1.5 saal tak dhoke mein rkha gya..fir ek din 14 June 2022 ko agnipath scheme ko launch Kiya gya or humse kaha gya ki aapki jo bhi recruitment kisi bhi stage par thi usko hum cancel krte hai..Hume iss recruitment k liye hrr sambhav prayas kiya hum Defence minister Rajnath Singh ji se bhi mile unhone Hume yeh aaswasan diya ki chinta mat kijiye aapki recruitment process ko hum complete krenge or aapko joining denge but woh apni baat se plat gye...sir humne bahut mehnat ki thii fooj ki wardi ko paane k liye...hum sab gareeb ghr k bcche hai...hamari recruitment ko cancel krne par desh mein 64+ bccho ne suicide krliya tha...hum aapse yeh aagrah krte hai ki aap hamare liye aawaj ko uthaiye..scheme launch hone se pehle hi recruitment ko complete krliya tha...sir kya fooj ka sapna dekhna yeh hamari sabse badi galti thii...hum roj ghut ghut k marte hai..khud ko face tak nhi krpate hai...jhaa humne khud ko ek fooj ka part bnte dekha thaa whaa par hum aaj majdoori krr rahe hai
 *Apki 1 vedio hmare घर में उजाला kr skti he प्लीज सर हमारे लिए वीडियो बना दो* 
Please sir hamari aawaj ko raise krne mein hamari help kijiye

अभ्यर्थियो ने फ़रवरी में राजनाथ सिंह की चुनावी रैलियों में जाकर शांतिपूर्ण तरीके से और लोकतांत्रिक तरीके से सेना भर्ती की मांग की। लेकिन सरकार के कानो में जूं तक नहीं रेंगी।

उसके बाद बिहार में शांतिपूर्ण तरीके से प्रदर्शन हुआ लेकिन सरकार ने कोई संज्ञान नहीं लिया।

सीकर से एक यूवा दिल्ली तक दौड़कर गया, टोंक मालपुरा से काफी अभ्यर्थी दिल्ली तक पैदल गए और शांतिपूर्ण और लोकतांत्रिक प्रक्रिया से सत्यग्रह किया लेकिन फिर भी सरकार ने नही सुनी।

8 मई को युवाओं ने शांतिपूर्ण तरीके से सेना भर्ती की मांग को लेकर भारत बंद किया लेकिन फिर भी कोई असर नहीं हुआ।

अभ्यर्थियों ने तिरंगा रैलियां निकाली फिर भी सरकार ने नही सुनी।

10-10 मिलियन तक ट्विटर पर सेना भर्ती प्रक्रिया शुरू करवाने के लेकर hashtags ट्रेंड करवाए फिर भी यह सरकार चुप रही।

अभी युवाओं के पास कोई option नही बचा इसलिए युवाओं ने यह रास्ता अपनाया है।

सर 1.5 लाख युवा का भविष्य आपके हाथ में हे 
14/june/2022 ko हमारी डिफेंस की *जॉइनिंग कैंसिल हो गई  गवर्नमेंट की Agniveer* योजना के कारण हमने आपको Mail भी करें पर आपने हमारी Mail देखी नही हे 
 hamari army /airforce ki recruitment 2019-22 k beech mein dekhi thii jiske liye humne bahut mehnat ki thi...hume baar baar dhoka diya gya sarkar k dwara ki jld hi aapki recruitment ko complete krdiya jayega Recruitment office's par vist krne par hume yeh kaha gya ki chinta mat kijiye aapko aapki joining mil jayegi sirf kuch administrative reason chl rahe hai...Aisa bol kr hume 1-1.5 saal tak dhoke mein rkha gya..fir ek din 14 June 2022 ko agnipath scheme ko launch Kiya gya or humse kaha gya ki aapki jo bhi recruitment kisi bhi stage par thi usko hum cancel krte hai..Hume iss recruitment k liye hrr sambhav prayas kiya hum Defence minister Rajnath Singh ji se bhi mile unhone Hume yeh aaswasan diya ki chinta mat kijiye aapki recruitment process ko hum complete krenge or aapko joining denge but woh apni baat se plat gye...sir humne bahut mehnat ki thii fooj ki wardi ko paane k liye...hum sab gareeb ghr k bcche hai...hamari recruitment ko cancel krne par desh mein 64+ bccho ne suicide krliya tha...hum aapse yeh aagrah krte hai ki aap hamare liye aawaj ko uthaiye..scheme launch hone se pehle hi recruitment ko complete krliya tha...sir kya fooj ka sapna dekhna yeh hamari sabse badi galti thii...hum roj ghut ghut k marte hai..khud ko face tak nhi krpate hai...jhaa humne khud ko ek fooj ka part bnte dekha thaa whaa par hum aaj majdoori krr rahe hai
 *Apki 1 vedio hmare घर में उजाला kr skti he प्लीज सर हमारे लिए वीडियो बना दो* 
Please sir hamari aawaj ko raise krne mein hamari help kijiye 
-(9877781662) Abhinav please

 hamari army /airforce ki recruitment 2019-22 k beech mein dekhi thii jiske liye humne bahut mehnat ki thi...hume baar baar dhoka diya gya sarkar k dwara ki jld hi aapki recruitment ko complete krdiya jayega Recruitment office's par vist krne par hume yeh kaha gya ki chinta mat kijiye aapko aapki joining mil jayegi sirf kuch administrative reason chl rahe hai...Aisa bol kr hume 1-1.5 saal tak dhoke mein rkha gya..fir ek din 14 June 2022 ko agnipath scheme ko launch Kiya gya or humse kaha gya ki aapki jo bhi recruitment kisi bhi stage par thi usko hum cancel krte hai..Hume iss recruitment k liye hrr sambhav prayas kiya hum Defence minister Rajnath Singh ji se bhi mile unhone Hume yeh aaswasan diya ki chinta mat kijiye aapki recruitment process ko hum complete krenge or aapko joining denge but woh apni baat se plat gye...sir humne bahut mehnat ki thii fooj ki wardi ko paane k liye...hum sab gareeb ghr k bcche hai...hamari recruitment ko cancel krne par desh mein 64+ bccho ne suicide krliya tha...hum aapse yeh aagrah krte hai ki aap hamare liye aawaj ko uthaiye..scheme launch hone se pehle hi recruitment ko complete krliya tha...sir kya fooj ka sapna dekhna yeh hamari sabse badi galti thii...hum roj ghut ghut k marte hai..khud ko face tak nhi krpate hai...jhaa humne khud ko ek fooj ka part bnte dekha thaa whaa par hum aaj majdoori krr rahe hai
 *Apki 1 vedio hmare घर में उजाला kr skti he प्लीज सर हमारे लिए वीडियो बना दो* 
Please sir hamari aawaj ko raise krne mein hamari help kijiye 
-(9877781662) Abhinav

सर हमने हमारी आर्मी/एयरफोर्स की भर्ती 2019-22 के बीच में देखी थी, जिसके लिए हमने बहुत मेहनत की थी... हमें बार-बार धोखा दिया गया सरकार के द्वारा की जल्द ही आपकी भर्ती पूरी हो जाएगी या आपको ज्वाइनिंग लेटर दे दिए जाएंगे... बार-बार साइट पर जाकर या फिर आर्मी भर्ती कार्यालय का दौरा करने पर हमें यह कहा गया कि चिंता मत कीजिए आपको आपकी ज्वाइनिंग मिल जाएगी सिर्फ कुछ प्रशासनिक कारण चल रहे हैं... ऐसा बोलकर हमें 1-1.5 साल तक धोखे में रखा गया.. फिर एक दिन 14 जून 2022 को अग्निपथ योजना शुरू की गई और हमसे कहा गया कि आपकी जो भी भर्ती चाहे किसी भी चरण पर थी उसको हम रद्द करते हैं.. सर हमने इस भर्ती के लिए हर संभव प्रयास किया था। हमने रक्षा मंत्री राजनाथ सिंह जी से भी मिले। उन्होंने हमने यह आश्वासन दिया कि चिंता मत कीजिए आपकी भर्ती प्रक्रिया को हम पूरा करेंगे या आपको ज्वाइनिंग देंगे लेकिन वो अपनी बात से मुकर गए... सर हमने बहुत मेहनत की थी इस फौज की वर्दी को पाने के लिए... हम सब गरीब घर के बच्चे हैं... हमारी भर्ती को रद्द करने पर देश में 64+ बच्चों ने आत्महत्या कर ली थी... हम आपसे यह आग्रह करते हैं कि आप हमारे लिए आवाज उठाएं... आज सब अग्निपथ के लिए बोल रहे है, लेकिन सर हमने तो अग्निपथ योजना शुरू होने से पहले ही भर्ती पूरी कर ली थी... सर क्या फौज का सपना देखना हमारी सबसे बड़ी गलती थी... हम रोज़ घुट घुट के मरते हैं.. खुद को फेस तक नहीं करते... हमने खुद को एक फौज का पार्ट बनते देखा

था, पर आज हम मज़दूरी कर रहे हैं... कृपया सर हमारी आवाज़ उठाने में हमारी मदद करें

 hamari army /airforce ki recruitment 2019-22 k beech mein dekhi thii jiske liye humne bahut mehnat ki thi...hume baar baar dhoka diya gya sarkar k dwara ki jld hi aapki recruitment ko complete krdiya jayega Recruitment office's par vist krne par hume yeh kaha gya ki chinta mat kijiye aapko aapki joining mil jayegi sirf kuch administrative reason chl rahe hai...Aisa bol kr hume 1-1.5 saal tak dhoke mein rkha gya..fir ek din 14 June 2022 ko agnipath scheme ko launch Kiya gya or humse kaha gya ki aapki jo bhi recruitment kisi bhi stage par thi usko hum cancel krte hai..Hume iss recruitment k liye hrr sambhav prayas kiya hum Defence minister Rajnath Singh ji se bhi mile unhone Hume yeh aaswasan diya ki chinta mat kijiye aapki recruitment process ko hum complete krenge or aapko joining denge but woh apni baat se plat gye...sir humne bahut mehnat ki thii fooj ki wardi ko paane k liye...hum sab gareeb ghr k bcche hai...hamari recruitment ko cancel krne par desh mein 64+ bccho ne suicide krliya tha...hum aapse yeh aagrah krte hai ki aap hamare liye aawaj ko uthaiye..scheme launch hone se pehle hi recruitment ko complete krliya tha...sir kya fooj ka sapna dekhna yeh hamari sabse badi galti thii...hum roj ghut ghut k marte hai..khud ko face tak nhi krpate hai...jhaa humne khud ko ek fooj ka part bnte dekha thaa whaa par hum aaj majdoori krr rahe hai

 hamari army /airforce ki recruitment 2019-22 k beech mein dekhi thii jiske liye humne bahut mehnat ki thi...hume baar baar dhoka diya gya sarkar k dwara ki jld hi aapki recruitment ko complete krdiya jayega Recruitment office's par vist krne par hume yeh kaha gya ki chinta mat kijiye aapko aapki joining mil jayegi sirf kuch administrative reason chl rahe hai...Aisa bol kr hume 1-1.5 saal tak dhoke mein rkha gya..fir ek din 14 June 2022 ko agnipath scheme ko launch Kiya gya or humse kaha gya ki aapki jo bhi recruitment kisi bhi stage par thi usko hum cancel krte hai..Hume iss recruitment k liye hrr sambhav prayas kiya hum Defence minister Rajnath Singh ji se bhi mile unhone Hume yeh aaswasan diya ki chinta mat kijiye aapki recruitment process ko hum complete krenge or aapko joining denge but woh apni baat se plat gye...sir humne bahut mehnat ki thii fooj ki wardi ko paane k liye...hum sab gareeb ghr k bcche hai...hamari recruitment ko cancel krne par desh mein 64+ bccho ne suicide krliya tha...hum aapse yeh aagrah krte hai ki aap hamare liye aawaj ko uthaiye..scheme launch hone se pehle hi recruitment ko complete krliya tha...sir kya fooj ka sapna dekhna yeh hamari sabse badi galti thii...hum roj ghut ghut k marte hai..khud ko face tak nhi krpate hai...jhaa humne khud ko ek fooj ka part bnte dekha thaa whaa par hum aaj majdoori krr rahe hai

सर 1.5 लाख युवा का भविष्य आपके हाथ में हे 
14/june/2022 ko हमारी डिफेंस की *जॉइनिंग कैंसिल हो गई  गवर्नमेंट की Agniveer* योजना के कारण हमने आपको Mail भी करें पर आपने हमारी Mail देखी नही हे 
 hamari army /airforce ki recruitment 2019-22 k beech mein dekhi thii jiske liye humne bahut mehnat ki thi...hume baar baar dhoka diya gya sarkar k dwara ki jld hi aapki recruitment ko complete krdiya jayega Recruitment office's par vist krne par hume yeh kaha gya ki chinta mat kijiye aapko aapki joining mil jayegi sirf kuch administrative reason chl rahe hai...Aisa bol kr hume 1-1.5 saal tak dhoke mein rkha gya..fir ek din 14 June 2022 ko agnipath scheme ko launch Kiya gya or humse kaha gya ki aapki jo bhi recruitment kisi bhi stage par thi usko hum cancel krte hai..Hume iss recruitment k liye hrr sambhav prayas kiya hum Defence minister Rajnath Singh ji se bhi mile unhone Hume yeh aaswasan diya ki chinta mat kijiye aapki recruitment process ko hum complete krenge or aapko joining denge but woh apni baat se plat gye...sir humne bahut mehnat ki thii fooj ki wardi ko paane k liye...hum sab gareeb ghr k bcche hai...hamari recruitment ko cancel krne par desh mein 64+ bccho ne suicide krliya tha...hum aapse yeh aagrah krte hai ki aap hamare liye aawaj ko uthaiye..scheme launch hone se pehle hi recruitment ko complete krliya tha...sir kya fooj ka sapna dekhna yeh hamari sabse badi galti thii...hum roj ghut ghut k marte hai..khud ko face tak nhi krpate hai...jhaa humne khud ko ek fooj ka part bnte dekha thaa whaa par hum aaj majdoori krr rahe hai
 *Apki 1 vedio hmare घर में उजाला kr skti he प्लीज सर हमारे लिए वीडियो बना दो* 
Please sir hamari aawaj ko raise krne mein hamari help kijiye

सर 1.5 लाख युवा का भविष्य आपके हाथ में हे 
14/june/2022 ko हमारी डिफेंस की *जॉइनिंग कैंसिल हो गई  गवर्नमेंट की Agniveer* योजना के कारण हमने आपको Mail भी करें पर आपने हमारी Mail देखी नही हे 
 hamari army /airforce ki recruitment 2019-22 k beech mein dekhi thii jiske liye humne bahut mehnat ki thi...hume baar baar dhoka diya gya sarkar k dwara ki jld hi aapki recruitment ko complete krdiya jayega Recruitment office's par vist krne par hume yeh kaha gya ki chinta mat kijiye aapko aapki joining mil jayegi sirf kuch administrative reason chl rahe hai...Aisa bol kr hume 1-1.5 saal tak dhoke mein rkha gya..fir ek din 14 June 2022 ko agnipath scheme ko launch Kiya gya or humse kaha gya ki aapki jo bhi recruitment kisi bhi stage par thi usko hum cancel krte hai..Hume iss recruitment k liye hrr sambhav prayas kiya hum Defence minister Rajnath Singh ji se bhi mile unhone Hume yeh aaswasan diya ki chinta mat kijiye aapki recruitment process ko hum complete krenge or aapko joining denge but woh apni baat se plat gye...sir humne bahut mehnat ki thii fooj ki wardi ko paane k liye...hum sab gareeb ghr k bcche hai...hamari recruitment ko cancel krne par desh mein 64+ bccho ne suicide krliya tha...hum aapse yeh aagrah krte hai ki aap hamare liye aawaj ko uthaiye..scheme launch hone se pehle hi recruitment ko complete krliya tha...sir kya fooj ka sapna dekhna yeh hamari sabse badi galti thii...hum roj ghut ghut k marte hai..khud ko face tak nhi krpate hai...jhaa humne khud ko ek fooj ka part bnte dekha thaa whaa par hum aaj majdoori krr rahe hai
 *Apki 1 vedio hmare घर में उजाला kr skti he प्लीज सर हमारे लिए वीडियो बना दो* 
Please sir hamari aawaj ko raise krne mein hamari help kijiye

14/june/2022 ko हमारी डिफेंस की *जॉइनिंग कैंसिल हो गई  गवर्नमेंट की Agniveer* योजना के कारण हमने आपको Mail भी करें पर आपने हमारी Mail देखी नही हे 
 hamari army /airforce ki recruitment 2019-22 k beech mein dekhi thii jiske liye humne bahut mehnat ki thi...hume baar baar dhoka diya gya sarkar k dwara ki jld hi aapki recruitment ko complete krdiya jayega Recruitment office's par vist krne par hume yeh kaha gya ki chinta mat kijiye aapko aapki joining mil jayegi sirf kuch administrative reason chl rahe hai...Aisa bol kr hume 1-1.5 saal tak dhoke mein rkha gya..fir ek din 14 June 2022 ko agnipath scheme ko launch Kiya gya or humse kaha gya ki aapki jo bhi recruitment kisi bhi stage par thi usko hum cancel krte hai..Hume iss recruitment k liye hrr sambhav prayas kiya hum Defence minister Rajnath Singh ji se bhi mile unhone Hume yeh aaswasan diya ki chinta mat kijiye aapki recruitment process ko hum complete krenge or aapko joining denge but woh apni baat se plat gye...sir humne bahut mehnat ki thii fooj ki wardi ko paane k liye...hum sab gareeb ghr k bcche hai...hamari recruitment ko cancel krne par desh mein 64+ bccho ne suicide krliya tha...hum aapse yeh aagrah krte hai ki aap hamare liye aawaj ko uthaiye..scheme launch hone se pehle hi recruitment ko complete krliya tha...sir kya fooj ka sapna dekhna yeh hamari sabse badi galti thii...hum roj ghut ghut k marte hai..khud ko face tak nhi krpate hai...jhaa humne khud ko ek fooj ka part bnte dekha thaa whaa par hum aaj majdoori krr rahe hai

 hamari army /airforce ki recruitment 2019-22 k beech mein dekhi thii jiske liye humne bahut mehnat ki thi...hume baar baar dhoka diya gya sarkar k dwara ki jld hi aapki recruitment ko complete krdiya jayega Recruitment office's par vist krne par hume yeh kaha gya ki chinta mat kijiye aapko aapki joining mil jayegi sirf kuch administrative reason chl rahe hai...Aisa bol kr hume 1-1.5 saal tak dhoke mein rkha gya..fir ek din 14 June 2022 ko agnipath scheme ko launch Kiya gya or humse kaha gya ki aapki jo bhi recruitment kisi bhi stage par thi usko hum cancel krte hai..Hume iss recruitment k liye hrr sambhav prayas kiya hum Defence minister Rajnath Singh ji se bhi mile unhone Hume yeh aaswasan diya ki chinta mat kijiye aapki recruitment process ko hum complete krenge or aapko joining denge but woh apni baat se plat gye...sir humne bahut mehnat ki thii fooj ki wardi ko paane k liye...hum sab gareeb ghr k bcche hai...hamari recruitment ko cancel krne par desh mein 64+ bccho ne suicide krliya tha...hum aapse yeh aagrah krte hai ki aap hamare liye aawaj ko uthaiye..scheme launch hone se pehle hi recruitment ko complete krliya tha...sir kya fooj ka sapna dekhna yeh hamari sabse badi galti thii...hum roj ghut ghut k marte hai..khud ko face tak nhi krpate hai...jhaa humne khud ko ek fooj ka part bnte dekha thaa whaa par hum aaj majdoori krr rahe hai
 *Apki 1 vedio hmare घर में उजाला kr skti he प्लीज सर हमारे लिए वीडियो बना दो* 
Please sir hamari aawaj ko raise krne mein hamari help kijiye 
-(9877781662) Abhinav

 hamari army /airforce ki recruitment 2019-22 k beech mein dekhi thii jiske liye humne bahut mehnat ki thi...hume baar baar dhoka diya gya sarkar k dwara ki jld hi aapki recruitment ko complete krdiya jayega Recruitment office's par vist krne par hume yeh kaha gya ki chinta mat kijiye aapko aapki joining mil jayegi sirf kuch administrative reason chl rahe hai...Aisa bol kr hume 1-1.5 saal tak dhoke mein rkha gya..fir ek din 14 June 2022 ko agnipath scheme ko launch Kiya gya or humse kaha gya ki aapki jo bhi recruitment kisi bhi stage par thi usko hum cancel krte hai..Hume iss recruitment k liye hrr sambhav prayas kiya hum Defence minister Rajnath Singh ji se bhi mile unhone Hume yeh aaswasan diya ki chinta mat kijiye aapki recruitment process ko hum complete krenge or aapko joining denge but woh apni baat se plat gye...sir humne bahut mehnat ki thii fooj ki wardi ko paane k liye...hum sab gareeb ghr k bcche hai...hamari recruitment ko cancel krne par desh mein 64+ bccho ne suicide krliya tha...hum aapse yeh aagrah krte hai ki aap hamare liye aawaj ko uthaiye..scheme launch hone se pehle hi recruitment ko complete krliya tha...sir kya fooj ka sapna dekhna yeh hamari sabse badi galti thii...hum roj ghut ghut k marte hai..khud ko face tak nhi krpate hai...jhaa humne khud ko ek fooj ka part bnte dekha thaa whaa par hum aaj majdoori krr rahe hai
 *Apki 1 vedio hmare घर में उजाला kr skti he प्लीज सर हमारे लिए वीडियो बना दो* 
Please sir hamari aawaj ko raise krne mein hamari help kijiye 
-(9877781662) Abhinav

14/june/2022 ko हमारी डिफेंस की *जॉइनिंग कैंसिल हो गई  गवर्नमेंट की Agniveer* योजना के कारण हमने आपको Mail भी करें पर आपने हमारी Mail देखी नही हे 
 hamari army /airforce ki recruitment 2019-22 k beech mein dekhi thii jiske liye humne bahut mehnat ki thi...hume baar baar dhoka diya gya sarkar k dwara ki jld hi aapki recruitment ko complete krdiya jayega Recruitment office's par vist krne par hume yeh kaha gya ki chinta mat kijiye aapko aapki joining mil jayegi sirf kuch administrative reason chl rahe hai...Aisa bol kr hume 1-1.5 saal tak dhoke mein rkha gya..fir ek din 14 June 2022 ko agnipath scheme ko launch Kiya gya or humse kaha gya ki aapki jo bhi recruitment kisi bhi stage par thi usko hum cancel krte hai..Hume iss recruitment k liye hrr sambhav prayas kiya hum Defence minister Rajnath Singh ji se bhi mile unhone Hume yeh aaswasan diya ki chinta mat kijiye aapki recruitment process ko hum complete krenge or aapko joining denge but woh apni baat se plat gye...sir humne bahut mehnat ki thii fooj ki wardi ko paane k liye...hum sab gareeb ghr k bcche hai...hamari recruitment ko cancel krne par desh mein 64+ bccho ne suicide krliya tha...hum aapse yeh aagrah krte hai ki aap hamare liye aawaj ko uthaiye..scheme launch hone se pehle hi recruitment ko complete krliya tha...sir kya fooj ka sapna dekhna yeh hamari sabse badi galti thii...hum roj ghut ghut k marte hai..khud ko face tak nhi krpate hai...jhaa humne khud ko ek fooj ka part bnte dekha thaa whaa par hum aaj majdoori krr rahe hai
 *Apki 1 vedio hmare घर में उजाला kr skti he प्लीज सर हमारे लिए वीडियो बना दो* 
Please sir hamari aawaj ko raise krne mein hamari help kijiye 
-(9877781662) Abhinav

 hamari army /airforce ki recruitment 2019-22 k beech mein dekhi thii jiske liye humne bahut mehnat ki thi...hume baar baar dhoka diya gya sarkar k dwara ki jld hi aapki recruitment ko complete krdiya jayega Recruitment office's par vist krne par hume yeh kaha gya ki chinta mat kijiye aapko aapki joining mil jayegi sirf kuch administrative reason chl rahe hai...Aisa bol kr hume 1-1.5 saal tak dhoke mein rkha gya..fir ek din 14 June 2022 ko agnipath scheme ko launch Kiya gya or humse kaha gya ki aapki jo bhi recruitment kisi bhi stage par thi usko hum cancel krte hai..Hume iss recruitment k liye hrr sambhav prayas kiya hum Defence minister Rajnath Singh ji se bhi mile unhone Hume yeh aaswasan diya ki chinta mat kijiye aapki recruitment process ko hum complete krenge or aapko joining denge but woh apni baat se plat gye...sir humne bahut mehnat ki thii fooj ki wardi ko paane k liye...hum sab gareeb ghr k bcche hai...hamari recruitment ko cancel krne par desh mein 64+ bccho ne suicide krliya tha...hum aapse yeh aagrah krte hai ki aap hamare liye aawaj ko uthaiye..scheme launch hone se pehle hi recruitment ko complete krliya tha...sir kya fooj ka sapna dekhna yeh hamari sabse badi galti thii...hum roj ghut ghut k marte hai..khud ko face tak nhi krpate hai...jhaa humne khud ko ek fooj ka part bnte dekha thaa whaa par hum aaj majdoori krr rahe hai
 *Apki 1 vedio hmare घर में उजाला kr skti he प्लीज सर हमारे लिए वीडियो बना दो* 
Please sir hamari aawaj ko raise krne mein hamari help kijiye 
-(9877781662) Abhinav

 hamari army /airforce ki recruitment 2019-22 k beech mein dekhi thii jiske liye humne bahut mehnat ki thi...hume baar baar dhoka diya gya sarkar k dwara ki jld hi aapki recruitment ko complete krdiya jayega Recruitment office's par vist krne par hume yeh kaha gya ki chinta mat kijiye aapko aapki joining mil jayegi sirf kuch administrative reason chl rahe hai...Aisa bol kr hume 1-1.5 saal tak dhoke mein rkha gya..fir ek din 14 June 2022 ko agnipath scheme ko launch Kiya gya or humse kaha gya ki aapki jo bhi recruitment kisi bhi stage par thi usko hum cancel krte hai..Hume iss recruitment k liye hrr sambhav prayas kiya hum Defence minister Rajnath Singh ji se bhi mile unhone Hume yeh aaswasan diya ki chinta mat kijiye aapki recruitment process ko hum complete krenge or aapko joining denge but woh apni baat se plat gye...sir humne bahut mehnat ki thii fooj ki wardi ko paane k liye...hum sab gareeb ghr k bcche hai...hamari recruitment ko cancel krne par desh mein 64+ bccho ne suicide krliya tha...hum aapse yeh aagrah krte hai ki aap hamare liye aawaj ko uthaiye..scheme launch hone se pehle hi recruitment ko complete krliya tha...sir kya fooj ka sapna dekhna yeh hamari sabse badi galti thii...hum roj ghut ghut k marte hai..khud ko face tak nhi krpate hai...jhaa humne khud ko ek fooj ka part bnte dekha thaa whaa par hum aaj majdoori krr rahe hai
 *Apki 1 vedio hmare घर में उजाला kr skti he प्लीज सर हमारे लिए वीडियो बना दो* 
Please sir hamari aawaj ko raise krne mein hamari help kijiye 
-(9877781662) Abhinav

14/june/2022 ko हमारी डिफेंस की *जॉइनिंग कैंसिल हो गई  गवर्नमेंट की Agniveer* योजना के कारण हमने आपको Mail भी करें पर आपने हमारी Mail देखी नही हे 
 hamari army /airforce ki recruitment 2019-22 k beech mein dekhi thii jiske liye humne bahut mehnat ki thi...hume baar baar dhoka diya gya sarkar k dwara ki jld hi aapki recruitment ko complete krdiya jayega Recruitment office's par vist krne par hume yeh kaha gya ki chinta mat kijiye aapko aapki joining mil jayegi sirf kuch administrative reason chl rahe hai...Aisa bol kr hume 1-1.5 saal tak dhoke mein rkha gya..fir ek din 14 June 2022 ko agnipath scheme ko launch Kiya gya or humse kaha gya ki aapki jo bhi recruitment kisi bhi stage par thi usko hum cancel krte hai..Hume iss recruitment k liye hrr sambhav prayas kiya hum Defence minister Rajnath Singh ji se bhi mile unhone Hume yeh aaswasan diya ki chinta mat kijiye aapki recruitment process ko hum complete krenge or aapko joining denge but woh apni baat se plat gye...sir humne bahut mehnat ki thii fooj ki wardi ko paane k liye...hum sab gareeb ghr k bcche hai...hamari recruitment ko cancel krne par desh mein 64+ bccho ne suicide krliya tha...hum aapse yeh aagrah krte hai ki aap hamare liye aawaj ko uthaiye..scheme launch hone se pehle hi recruitment ko complete krliya tha...sir kya fooj ka sapna dekhna yeh hamari sabse badi galti thii...hum roj ghut ghut k marte hai..khud ko face tak nhi krpate hai...jhaa humne khud ko ek fooj ka part bnte dekha thaa whaa par hum aaj majdoori krr rahe hai
 *Apki 1 vedio hmare घर में उजाला kr skti he प्लीज सर हमारे लिए वीडियो बना दो* 
Please sir hamari aawaj ko raise krne mein hamari help kijiye 
-(9877781662) Abhinav

14/june/2022 ko हमारी डिफेंस की *जॉइनिंग कैंसिल हो गई  गवर्नमेंट की Agniveer* योजना के कारण हमने आपको Mail भी करें पर आपने हमारी Mail देखी नही हे 
 hamari army /airforce ki recruitment 2019-22 k beech mein dekhi thii jiske liye humne bahut mehnat ki thi...hume baar baar dhoka diya gya sarkar k dwara ki jld hi aapki recruitment ko complete krdiya jayega Recruitment office's par vist krne par hume yeh kaha gya ki chinta mat kijiye aapko aapki joining mil jayegi sirf kuch administrative reason chl rahe hai...Aisa bol kr hume 1-1.5 saal tak dhoke mein rkha gya..fir ek din 14 June 2022 ko agnipath scheme ko launch Kiya gya or humse kaha gya ki aapki jo bhi recruitment kisi bhi stage par thi usko hum cancel krte hai..Hume iss recruitment k liye hrr sambhav prayas kiya hum Defence minister Rajnath Singh ji se bhi mile unhone Hume yeh aaswasan diya ki chinta mat kijiye aapki recruitment process ko hum complete krenge or aapko joining denge but woh apni baat se plat gye...sir humne bahut mehnat ki thii fooj ki wardi ko paane k liye...hum sab gareeb ghr k bcche hai...hamari recruitment ko cancel krne par desh mein 64+ bccho ne suicide krliya tha...hum aapse yeh aagrah krte hai ki aap hamare liye aawaj ko uthaiye..scheme launch hone se pehle hi recruitment ko complete krliya tha...sir kya fooj ka sapna dekhna yeh hamari sabse badi galti thii...hum roj ghut ghut k marte hai..khud ko face tak nhi krpate hai...jhaa humne khud ko ek fooj ka part bnte dekha thaa whaa par hum aaj majdoori krr rahe hai

 hamari army /airforce ki recruitment 2019-22 k beech mein dekhi thii jiske liye humne bahut mehnat ki thi...hume baar baar dhoka diya gya sarkar k dwara ki jld hi aapki recruitment ko complete krdiya jayega Recruitment office's par vist krne par hume yeh kaha gya ki chinta mat kijiye aapko aapki joining mil jayegi sirf kuch administrative reason chl rahe hai...Aisa bol kr hume 1-1.5 saal tak dhoke mein rkha gya..fir ek din 14 June 2022 ko agnipath scheme ko launch Kiya gya or humse kaha gya ki aapki jo bhi recruitment kisi bhi stage par thi usko hum cancel krte hai..Hume iss recruitment k liye hrr sambhav prayas kiya hum Defence minister Rajnath Singh ji se bhi mile unhone Hume yeh aaswasan diya ki chinta mat kijiye aapki recruitment process ko hum complete krenge or aapko joining denge but woh apni baat se plat gye...sir humne bahut mehnat ki thii fooj ki wardi ko paane k liye...hum sab gareeb ghr k bcche hai...hamari recruitment ko cancel krne par desh mein 64+ bccho ne suicide krliya tha...hum aapse yeh aagrah krte hai ki aap hamare liye aawaj ko uthaiye..scheme launch hone se pehle hi recruitment ko complete krliya tha...sir kya fooj ka sapna dekhna yeh hamari sabse badi galti thii...hum roj ghut ghut k marte hai..khud ko face tak nhi krpate hai...jhaa humne khud ko ek fooj ka part bnte dekha thaa whaa par hum aaj majdoori krr rahe hai
 *Apki 1 vedio hmare घर में उजाला kr skti he प्लीज सर हमारे लिए वीडियो बना दो* 
Please sir hamari aawaj ko raise krne mein hamari help kijiye

 hamari army /airforce ki recruitment 2019-22 k beech mein dekhi thii jiske liye humne bahut mehnat ki thi...hume baar baar dhoka diya gya sarkar k dwara ki jld hi aapki recruitment ko complete krdiya jayega Recruitment office's par vist krne par hume yeh kaha gya ki chinta mat kijiye aapko aapki joining mil jayegi sirf kuch administrative reason chl rahe hai...Aisa bol kr hume 1-1.5 saal tak dhoke mein rkha gya..fir ek din 14 June 2022 ko agnipath scheme ko launch Kiya gya or humse kaha gya ki aapki jo bhi recruitment kisi bhi stage par thi usko hum cancel krte hai..Hume iss recruitment k liye hrr sambhav prayas kiya hum Defence minister Rajnath Singh ji se bhi mile unhone Hume yeh aaswasan diya ki chinta mat kijiye aapki recruitment process ko hum complete krenge or aapko joining denge but woh apni baat se plat gye...sir humne bahut mehnat ki thii fooj ki wardi ko paane k liye...hum sab gareeb ghr k bcche hai...hamari recruitment ko cancel krne par desh mein 64+ bccho ne suicide krliya tha...hum aapse yeh aagrah krte hai ki aap hamare liye aawaj ko uthaiye..scheme launch hone se pehle hi recruitment ko complete krliya tha...sir kya fooj ka sapna dekhna yeh hamari sabse badi galti thii...hum roj ghut ghut k marte hai..khud ko face tak nhi krpate hai...jhaa humne khud ko ek fooj ka part bnte dekha thaa whaa par hum aaj majdoori krr rahe hai
 *Apki 1 vedio hmare घर में उजाला kr skti he प्लीज सर हमारे लिए वीडियो बना दो* 
Please sir hamari aawaj ko raise krne mein hamari help kijiye 
-(9877781662) Abhinav

14/june/2022 ko हमारी डिफेंस की *जॉइनिंग कैंसिल हो गई  गवर्नमेंट की Agniveer* योजना के कारण हमने आपको Mail भी करें पर आपने हमारी Mail देखी नही हे 
 hamari army /airforce ki recruitment 2019-22 k beech mein dekhi thii jiske liye humne bahut mehnat ki thi...hume baar baar dhoka diya gya sarkar k dwara ki jld hi aapki recruitment ko complete krdiya jayega Recruitment office's par vist krne par hume yeh kaha gya ki chinta mat kijiye aapko aapki joining mil jayegi sirf kuch administrative reason chl rahe hai...Aisa bol kr hume 1-1.5 saal tak dhoke mein rkha gya..fir ek din 14 June 2022 ko agnipath scheme ko launch Kiya gya or humse kaha gya ki aapki jo bhi recruitment kisi bhi stage par thi usko hum cancel krte hai..Hume iss recruitment k liye hrr sambhav prayas kiya hum Defence minister Rajnath Singh ji se bhi mile unhone Hume yeh aaswasan diya ki chinta mat kijiye aapki recruitment process ko hum complete krenge or aapko joining denge but woh apni baat se plat gye...sir humne bahut mehnat ki thii fooj ki wardi ko paane k liye...hum sab gareeb ghr k bcche hai...hamari recruitment ko cancel krne par desh mein 64+ bccho ne suicide krliya tha...hum aapse yeh aagrah krte hai ki aap hamare liye aawaj ko uthaiye..scheme launch hone se pehle hi recruitment ko complete krliya tha...sir kya fooj ka sapna dekhna yeh hamari sabse badi galti thii...hum roj ghut ghut k marte hai..khud ko face tak nhi krpate hai...jhaa humne khud ko ek fooj ka part bnte dekha thaa whaa par hum aaj majdoori krr rahe hai
 *Apki 1 vedio hmare घर में उजाला kr skti he प्लीज सर हमारे लिए वीडियो बना दो* 
Please sir hamari aawaj ko raise krne mein hamari help kijiye

Dear Dhruv,

We hope this message finds you well. We are N.I.O.S D.EL.Ed candidates, and we are writing on behalf of the N.I.O.S D.El.Ed teachers from across the country. We are facing a critical issue that has affected approximately 14 lakh untrained teachers who were employed in government and private primary schools across India. Your platform has the power to bring our plight to the forefront, and we earnestly request your support in ventilating our voice throughout India.

Background Information:

With due respect, we would like to inform you that we are N.I.O.S D.El.Ed Teachers from across the country. According to the RTE-2009, every child has the fundamental right to receive primary education from a trained teacher. To ensure the fundamental rights of children, the Indian government passed a bill in both houses of Parliament with consensus in 2017. Through this, government, government-aided, and private school teachers who were untrained as of the 2010 NCTE notification were given the opportunity to complete the D.El.Ed course through NIOS. Thereafter, the Ministry of Human Resource Development (MHRD) issued a letter to all the Secretaries of States and Union Territories, directing that all teachers in government schools must possess minimum qualifications as mandated under the Right to Education Act, 2009, and a last chance was given to all teachers to acquire the same by March 31, 2019.

In 2017, the Modi government urged us to enroll in the Diploma in Elementary Education (D.El.Ed) conducted by N.I.O.S. Approximately 14 lakh untrained teachers, who were already employed in government and private primary schools across the country, enrolled. Subsequently, NCTE issued a recognition order to be published in the Gazette, thereby conducting the D.El.Ed program through the Open and Distance Learning (ODL) mode by NIOS, which reduced the duration of the program from 2 years to 18 months. Education Minister Prakash Javadekar (at that time) and our PM Narendra Damodardas Modi emphasized our enrollment in the Diploma in Elementary Education (D.El.Ed) through the National Institute of Open Schooling (NIOS). Normally, the program of the course is 2 years (18 months of theory and 6 months of internship), but our course was completed within 2 sessions (18 months) as we were already employed and did not require an internship. NIOS Board conducted all the exams for this course. It was promoted by Prime Minister Narendra Modi.

Current Situation:

According to the rules, this new plan of NCTE and the Modi government had to be published in the Gazette, but NCTE did not comply. As a result, in 2023, after 7 years, the Honourable Supreme Court announced that our degree is not valid for new recruitment. We cannot apply for any new recruitment in government schools and will not be able to do so in the future due to the negligence of NCTE and the false guarantee by Modi. Due to this mistake by Narendra Modi, today, 14 lakh families are suffering, with no solution in sight.

Our Request:

We, the 14 lakh affected teachers, humbly request your support to highlight our situation on your channel. Your influence and reach can help us gain the attention of the authorities and the public, potentially leading to a resolution of our predicament. We believe that with your help, we can bring our issue to the forefront and seek justice for the countless teachers who have dedicated their lives to educating the children of our country.

Thank you for your time and consideration. We sincerely hope that you will be able to support us in this crucial matter.

Warm regards,

N.I.O.S D.EL.Ed SONGAMI MONCHO
